Name: Just Enough Tales (JET)
Description: Browse all items with search, categories, recipes and uses. Commands: /jet (Adventure) - open item browser | /pinned (Adventure) - view pinned items | WIP: /jetsettings (Adventure) - open settings GUI | WIP: /recipehud (Adventure) - pin/unpin recipes to HUD overlay | WIP: /jetbind (Creative) - toggle O key binding
